Package com.jogamp.graph.ui.shapes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseButton
    An abstract GraphUI base filled button GraphShape, usually used as a backdrop or base shape for more informative button types.
    Button
    A GraphUI text labeled BaseButton GraphShape
    CrossHair
    A GraphUI Crosshair GraphShape
    GLButton
    A GraphUI GLEventListener based TexSeqButton GraphShape.
    GlyphShape
    Representing a single Font.Glyph as a GraphShape A GlyphShape is represented in font em-size [0..1] unscaled w/ bottom-left origin at 0/0 while preserving an intended position, see GlyphShape.getOrigPos() and GlyphShape.getOrigPos(float).
    ImageButton
    A GraphUI ImageSequence based TexSeqButton GraphShape.
    Label
    A GraphUI text label GraphShape
    MediaButton
    A GraphUI GLMediaPlayer based TexSeqButton GraphShape.
    Rectangle
    A GraphUI rectangle GraphShape
    TexSeqButton
    An abstract GraphUI TextureSequence BaseButton GraphShape.
